metadata.name: J48BAGEN #c5d789f3-be74-4dc6-9382-106f81bb839a
metadata.description: J48BAGEN is an AI text-to-image generator built on a model from 1000s of sketches from artist HybridGAN. Images are generated by the the user’s own text prompt in conjunction with the AI model. The collection is an experiment in community curation—in its final form, it will be an amalgamation of AI, artist, and participant synergy and symbiosis.
